   <concept id="FAR_5_705" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">5.705</ph> Publicizing postaward.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d370e8" class="- topic/p ">Follow usual publication procedures at <xref href="5.301.dita#FAR_5_301"
                  base="i1120562"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">5.301</xref>, except that the
following supersede the exceptions at <xref href="5.301.dita#FAR_5_301"
                  base="i1120562"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">5.301</xref>(b)(2) through (7):</p>
         <ol id="d356e28" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e18">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d356e38" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e23">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> Publicize the
award notice for any action exceeding $500,000, funded in whole
or in part by the Recovery Act, including-</p>
                     <ol id="d356e48" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e29">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph> Contracts;</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e34">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph> Modifications
to existing contracts;</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e39">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph> Orders
which are issued under task or delivery order contracts; and</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e44">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iv)</ph> Modifications
to orders under task or delivery order contracts.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e49">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> Contracting
officers shall identify contract actions, funded in whole or in
part by the Recovery Act, by using the following instructions which
are also available in the Recovery FAQS under "Buyers/Engineers"
at the Governmentwide Point of Entry (GPE) (
                           <xref href="https://www.sam.gov"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">https://www.sam.gov</xref>
                           
                        ):</p>
                     <ol id="d356e99" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e58">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph> If
submitting notices electronically via ftp or email, enter the word
"Recovery" as the first word in the title field.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e63">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph> If using
the GPE directly, select the "yes" radio button for the "Is this
a Recovery and Reinvestment Act action" field on the "Notice Details"
form (Step 2) located below the "NAICS Code" field. In addition,
enter the word "Recovery" as the first word in the title field.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e68">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph> In preparing
the description required by <xref href="5.207.dita#FAR_5_207"
                              base="i1120855"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.207</xref>(a)(16),
use clear and concise language to describe the planned procurement.
Use descriptions of the goods and services (including construction),
that can be understood by the general public. Avoid the use of acronyms
or terminology that is not widely understood by the general public.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e76">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Regardless
of dollar value, if the contract action, including all modifications
and orders under task or delivery order contracts, is not both fixed-price
and competitively awarded, publicize the award notice and include
in the description the rationale for using other than a fixed-priced
and/or competitive approach. Include in the description a statement
specifically noting if the contract action was not awarded competitively,
or was not fixed-price, or was neither competitive nor fixed-price.
These notices and the rationale will be available to the public
at the GPE, so do not include any proprietary information or information
that would compromise national security. The following table provides
examples for when a rationale is required.</p>
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e80" outputclass="Ctr">
                  <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Posting of Rationale - Examples</b>
               </p>
               <table frame="all" colsep="1" rowsep="1" class="- topic/table ">
                  <tgroup cols="3"
                          colsep="1"
                          rowsep="1"
                          outputclass="Notitle_rule"
                          class="- topic/tgroup ">
                     <colspec colnum="1" colname="1" colwidth="9*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                     <colspec colnum="2" colname="2" colwidth="46*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                     <colspec colnum="3" colname="3" colwidth="46*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                     <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                        <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry colname="1"
                                  align="center"
                                  outputclass="CellHeading_Ctr"
                                  class="- topic/entry "/>
                           <entry colname="2"
                                  align="center"
                                  outputclass="CellHeading_CtrSmallCaps"
                                  xtrc="SmallCaps"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Description
of Contract Action</b>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="3"
                                  align="center"
                                  outputclass="CellHeading_CtrSmallCaps"
                                  xtrc="SmallCaps"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Rationale
Required</b>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p outputclass="Ctr" class="- topic/p ">(1)</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="2"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">A
contract is competitively awarded and is fixed-price.</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="3"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Not
required.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p outputclass="Ctr" class="- topic/p ">(2)</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="2"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">A
contract is awarded that is not fixed-price.</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="3"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Required.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p outputclass="Ctr" class="- topic/p ">(3)</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="2"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">A
contract is awarded without competition.</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="3"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Required.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p outputclass="Ctr" class="- topic/p ">(4)</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="2"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">An
order is issued under a new or existing single award IDIQ contract.</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="3"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Required
if order is made under a contract described in paragraph (b)(2)
or (3) of this section.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p outputclass="Ctr" class="- topic/p ">(5)</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="2"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">An
order is issued under a new or existing multiple award IDIQ contract.</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="3"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Required
if one or both of the following conditions exist: (i) The order
is not fixed-price. (ii) The order is awarded pursuant to an exception
to the competition requirements applicable to the underlying vehicle
(<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i>, award is made pursuant to an exception to the fair
opportunity process).</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p outputclass="Ctr" class="- topic/p ">(6)</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="2"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">A
modification is issued.</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="3"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Required
if modification is made- (i) To a contract described in (b)(2) or
(3) of this section; or (ii) To an order requiring posting as described
in (b)(4) or (5) of this section.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="0" class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p outputclass="Ctr" class="- topic/p ">(7)</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="2"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">A
contract or order is awarded pursuant to a small business contracting
authority (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i>, SBAâ€™s section 8(a) program).</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry colname="3"
                                  align="left"
                                  outputclass="CellBody_Left"
                                  class="- topic/entry ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Required
if one or both of the following conditions exist: (i) the contract
or order is not fixed-price; (ii) the contract or order was not
awarded using competition (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i>, a non-competitive 8(a) award).</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d370e177">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> Contracting
officers shall use the instructions available in the Recovery FAQs
under "Buyers/Engineers" at the GPE (
                     <xref href="https://www.sam.gov"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">https://www.sam.gov</xref>
                     
                  )
to identify actions funded in whole or in part by the Recovery Act.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
